  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[and commit new felonies.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[However, a death would not be of any more use to those affected and their relatives than if the felon receives a long sentence.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[Plus we don't live in medieval times anymore.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[Handing out capital punishment is unethical.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[We don't need it.]]></edu>
